{"word":"συζητέω","slug":"συζητέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συζητέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ζητέω\">ζητέω</a></el>] ‘engage in serious conversation about a matter’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on amiable exchange of ideas, <b>discuss <a href='B:480 1:27'>Mk 1:27</a>; <a href='B:480 9:10'>9:10</a>; <a href='B:490 24:15'>Lk 24:15</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on contentious aspect, <b>dispute, argue, debate <a href='B:480 8:11'>Mk 8:11</a>; <a href='B:480 9:14'>9:14</a>, <a href='B:480 9:16'>16</a>; <a href='B:480 12:28'>12:28</a>; <a href='B:490 22:23'>Lk 22:23</a>; <a href='B:510 6:9'>Ac 6:9</a>; <a href='B:510 9:29'>9:29</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συζεύγνυμι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συζήτησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}